{"tid":101073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【旺角夜市】最後一夜 支那客讚香港獨有：沒像別人說那麼亂","createTime":"2017-01-30T14:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T18:37:10.000Z","uid":37661,"like":8,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a6b6cddc07de5140a2ab3248419ad20e5f6ad207","tid":101073,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:12:42.000Z","msg":"【旺角夜市】最後一夜 支那客讚香港獨有：沒像別人說那麼亂<br />\n<br />\n旺角夜市來到最後一晚，砵蘭街近朗豪坊一帶晚上7時許已瀰漫炭烤香味。可惜天公不造美，不時下起驟雨，但無阻約20檔小販及約500名市民、遊客到場，部分小販需一邊撐傘，一邊售賣小食，約20名警員在附近邏巡，整體秩序大致良好。<br />\n<br />\n來自支那河南的張女士說，已來過香港幾次，但首次在港過年，有本地人推薦旺角夜市，故特別到場一嚐本土風味。她認為氣氛熱鬧，是香港獨有景象，「大陸過支春是一家團圓，在家裡過，沒有像你這邊街上很熱鬧」。她說，下雨無影響心情，知道去年曾發生旺角騷亂，但不擔心安全，「覺得香港沒有像別人說的那麼亂」。<br />\n<br />\n23歲的呂小姐今年首次光顧，覺得氣氛熱鬧，認為下雨對她無影響，「平時好少有得食，呢度嘅嘢食好有本土特色，例如臭豆腐、魚蛋咁」。她又稱，去年的旺角騷亂是因特首梁振英而起，梁今年已宣佈不競逐連任，所以相信今年不會再發生騷亂，「佢親中，最唔鐘意呢啲本地嘢」。<br />\n<br />\n另一市民28歲的Drake稱，上年騷亂時並不在場，不擔心今年再發生同類事件，「今年食環署收斂咗好多，上年都係食環署想清咗啲小販，先搞到咁僵」。他又說，今年整體氣氛很好，會將小食當晚餐，「會盡量掃晒咁多檔」<br />\n<br />\n呂小姐<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170130/large/1485782996_bc3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170130%2Flarge%2F1485782996_bc3f.jpg&h=aabef694&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那河南的張女士<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170130/large/1485782994_514c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170130%2Flarge%2F1485782994_514c.jpg&h=0a07bea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170130/56242116\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170130%2F56242116&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=cc6aa6fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170130%2F56242116&h=a1e70707\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170130/56242116</a>"},{"pid":"17c013dc928e7baed78f19abbff62f81d492297b","tid":101073,"uid":45766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:15:04.000Z","msg":"好撚亂!為你好千其唔好來呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb58825306906ee105c2756caa4e8adfbbb86203","tid":101073,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:16:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚亂!為你好千其唔好來呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇人講咁亂=&gt;都係亂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16385e4932b0caf47f7347c361c68468964ae1e","tid":101073,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:37:53.000Z","msg":"冇左桂林夜市腸粉<br />\n<br />\n滿街擺賣二手垃圾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家買左二手豉油二手奶粉二手鞋未？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7c2a7b9617a28cb3334035f3463c08f3c0dd01","tid":101073,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:45:39.000Z","msg":"呂小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d463d5a7f47e1c58b965beacf445caa1a4795dae","tid":101073,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:47:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呂小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n被失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb19b74af50d6516788698b7bc76f9d102e54610","tid":101073,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:51:42.000Z","msg":"仆街了"},{"pid":"af9f77bb5c1b20cb63253bce1dd9ba58234bf91c","tid":101073,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c